{
  "stem": "4345.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My dad was-- you could see the depression in their faces.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And you know, all of a sudden, you hear that we cannot go to school anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "School had stopped for us until the-- we didn't finish anymore, the ending of the school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were-- even before the Nazis came in-- they already expelled us from school, the Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I never finished my fifth grade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So you were in the fifth grade?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the fifth grade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it-- in June-- I think June or beginning-- I don't know how it worked in-- in-- or beginning of July.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that school ended early July or late June, something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- and I remember, I said to Mommy-- I said, Mama, what is happening?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why are you so upset?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why-- why don't you look good?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't have any more-- we didn't have food in the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We could not go into a store anymore and buy food, because the-- the Gentiles would not sell it to us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Jewish people could not get any more food into the stores.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They could anymore go buy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whatever they had, they probably saved for themselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it left us, except if Mommy had flour, she would bake a cake or bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was very scarce.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were very religious, very strict.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mommy wore a sheitel, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I remember my little brother, Nahman, you know, in the picture there-- he came in one day to the house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he says, Mommy, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yanic ?] [INAUDIBLE], this was our neighbors in the backyard-- is eating bread with the [INAUDIBLE], the pig fat, that white stuff.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he offered me a piece.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Mommy, I'm hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What do you think I should do?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
